T02TD3764E:116b-3: mandal gyi cho ga / sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3764E:116b-4: gdod nas zhi ba'i chos kun dang //
T02TD3764E:116b-5: gang gi rang bzhin med par ni //
T02TD3764E:116b-6: sems ni ri rab ltar gnas pa //
T02TD3764E:116b-7: de la bden pa mthong zhes brjod //
T02TD3764E:116b-8: dam pa'i chos klog pa la sogs pa dang /
T02TD3764E:116b-9: bla ma'i mandal gyi cho ga ni /
T02TD3764E:116b-10: aom badzra bh'u mi a'a:h'um zhes brjod pas sems bskyed pa sngon du 'gro ba'i sgo nas lci ba chu dang bcas pas sa phyogs byug par bya'o //
T02TD3764E:116b-11: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su me tog bzhag ste /
T02TD3764E:116b-12: aom badzra re khe a'a:h'um zhes bya bas ni byin gyis brlab par bya'o //
T02TD3764E:116b-13: de nas me tog dgram pa'i sngags ni /
T02TD3764E:116b-14: aom ham ma h'a me ra be na ma:/
T02TD3764E:116b-16: aom yam p'urba bi de h'a ya na ma:/
T02TD3764E:116b-18: aom ram dzam bu dv'i p'a ya na ma:/
T02TD3764E:116b-20: aom lam aa pa ra go d'a ni ye na ma:/
T02TD3764E:116b-22: aom bam autta ra ku ra be na ma:/
T02TD3764E:116b-24: aom ya:au pa dv'i p'a ya na ma:/
T02TD3764E:116b-26: shar phyogs kyi mtshams g-yas g-yon gnyis su me tog gi tshom bu dgod do //
T02TD3764E:116b-28: aom ra:au pa dv'i p'a ya na ma:/
T02TD3764E:116b-29: 'dis lho phyogs kyi g-yas g-yon du'o //
T02TD3764E:116b-30: aom la:au pa dv'i p'a ya na ma:/
T02TD3764E:116b-31: nub phyogs kyi g-yas g-yon du'o //
T02TD3764E:116b-32: aom ba:au pa dv'i p'a ya na ma:/
T02TD3764E:116b-33: byang phyogs kyi g-yas g-yon du'o //
T02TD3764E:116b-34: de nas nang gi phyogs dang mtshams su'o //
T02TD3764E:116b-35: aom ya ga dza ra tan'a ya na ma:/
T02TD3764E:116b-36: aom ra pu ru sha ratn'a ya na ma:/
T02TD3764E:116b-37: aom la aa shva ratn'a ya na ma:/
T02TD3764E:116b-38: aom ba str'i tn'a ya na ma:/
T02TD3764E:116b-39: aom y'a khadga ratn'a ya na ma:/
T02TD3764E:116b-40: aom r'a ma ni ratn'a ya na ma:/
T02TD3764E:116b-41: aom l'a tsakra ratn'a ya na ma:/
T02TD3764E:116b-42: aom b'a sarba ni dhi bhyo nam:/
T02TD3764E:116b-43: shar nas bzung ste g-yas skor du phyogs mtshams brgyad du bskor bar bya'o //
T02TD3764E:116b-44: nang gi shar dang nub tu /
T02TD3764E:116b-47: 'di rnams kyis ni gling bzhi gling phran brgyad /
T02TD3764E:116b-48: rin po che sna bdun gter chen po dang brgyad /
T02TD3764E:116b-49: ri rab nyi zla dang bcas pa rin po che sna tshogs kyis bkang bar dmigs te sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'am /
T02TD3764E:116b-50: chos sam bla ma gang yang rung ba la dbul bar bsam mo //
T02TD3764E:117a-0: phan yon dpag tu med pa @117a * //
T02TD3764E:117a-1: yod de gzhung gzhan nas shes par bya'o //
T02TD3764E:117a-2: bla ma dang sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' la sogs pa'i mdun du bsnyen bkur bya'o //
T02TD3764E:117a-3: mandal gyi cho ga dngos grub brnyes pa'i slob dpon mkhas pa chen po rin chen 'byung gnas sbas pa'i zhal snga nas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD3764E:117a-5: // / mtshan yongs su grags par gyur pa dge bshes rdo rje gdan pas mdzad pa lags so //
T02TD3764E:117a-6: zhu chen gyi lo ts'a ba dge slong dar ma grags kyis bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa /
T02TD3764E:117a-7: pha rol tu phyin pa'i theg pa'i mandal gyi cho ga'o /
